name: I'm Late (Fax37)
description:
Made for the Trijam#82 : Delay in 5 Hours (first version)

Current version is 5h30.

I don't have enough time to put sounds, my regret. I also planned to make more levels but...

Hope you enjoy this entry.

Story and gameplay

In this game, you have to help the white rabbit to reach the gate as fast as possible by putting action elements on the level.

Simply drag and drop elements from UI to level.

What i do

I realize all the sprites and the code during the 5h except the background (from asset pack)
